<ab facs="#facs_176_r1l18">in <expan>ewer<ex>er</ex></expan> ſtat gemant habt auf <expan>ſymo<ex>n</ex>ıs</expan> et Jude ſchıerıſt nach auſʒ = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_176_r1l19"><expan>weıſu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> / <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> brıefs etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
